member.example:
This method should be invoked like this:


app.UseEndpoints(
    endpoints =>
    {
        // (...)

        endpoints.MapConfigurationAnalyzer();
    });
app.UseEndpoints(
    endpoints =>
    {
        // (...)

        endpoints.MapConfigurationAnalyzer("/my-route");
    });

This method should be invoked like this:


app.UseEndpoints(
    endpoints =>
    {
        // (...)

        endpoints.MapRouteAnalyzer();
    });
app.UseEndpoints(
    endpoints =>
    {
        // (...)

        endpoints.MapRouteAnalyzer("/my-route");
    });
